# Branch naming

Before creating a branch, **ask the user for the title** (short slug). Do not invent the slug.

- Bugfix: `bugs/<title-they-give>`
- Feature work: `feature/<title-they-give>`

Example: user says “integrate onboarding api” → `feature/integrate-onboarding-api`.
